'''FC Dynamo-2 Kyiv''' is a [[Ukraine|Ukrainian]] [[association football|football]] team based in [[Kiev]] (or Kyiv), [[Ukraine]]. The club was inaugurated in 1946. The club has been featured regularly in the [[Ukrainian First League]], since it cannot be promoted to the [[Ukrainian Premier League]], being a reserve team from the [[FC Dynamo Kyiv]] franchise. Like most tributary teams, the best players are sent up to the senior team, meanwhile developing other players for further call-ups.
